		<element kind="staticText" uuid="cd4d6bc6-08a1-4397-bf2c-b2560c24f3a8" x="15" y="75" width="350" height="17" fontSize="6.0" bold="true">
			<text><![CDATA[All sales are final : Once customers make a purchase, they will not be able to return that item for a replacement or refund. These policies typically apply to clearance and sale items.]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="30146d31-37f7-49ce-b3a4-37f2ac774851" x="15" y="108" width="350" height="17" fontSize="6.0" bold="true">
			<text><![CDATA[ No cash refund policy: No monetary refunds will be given for any reason, though alternative  refunds may be offered, such as store credit or exchanges]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="f7bb94db-b51a-4546-bbbb-1fb1e6bbdf6c" x="15" y="92" width="335" height="16" fontSize="6.0" bold="true">
			<text><![CDATA[No refunds. Exchange only: Customers may exchange items they wish to return, but they cannot get a monetary refund]]></text>
		</element>
